questions.statement:
&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Select the option that is related to the third word in the same way as the second word is related to the first.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;HEA : AHD :: TER : ?&lt;/p&gt;<br>&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;उस विकल्प का चयन करें जो तीसरे शब्द से उसी प्रकार संबंधित है जैसे दूसरा शब्द, पहले से संबंधित है।&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;HEA : AHD :: TER : ?&lt;/p&gt;

questions.explanation:
&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;The positional value table is as follows:&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/20/12/Common_Diagram_28.01.2020_D1.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 536px; height: 128px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The logic followed here is:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The letters of the second word are changed in the following manner-&lt;br /&gt;
Consonants - (-7) in the positional value&lt;br /&gt;
Vowels - (+3) in the positional value&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;HEA : AHD&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/23/02/F1_SSC_Mrunal_20.02.2023_D25.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 115px; height: 137px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;TER : MHK&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/23/02/F1_SSC_Mrunal_20.02.2023_D26.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 117px; height: 136px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Hence, the correct answer is &amp;quot;None of the above&amp;quot;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;स्थितीय&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;मानों की&amp;nbsp;तालिका इस प्रकार है:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/20/12/Common_Diagram_28.01.2020_D1.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 536px; height: 128px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;यहाँ अनुसरण किया गया तर्क इस प्रकार&amp;nbsp;है:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;दूसरे शब्द के अक्षर इस प्रकार बदले जाते हैं-&lt;br /&gt;
व्यंजन - (-7) &lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;स्थितीय&lt;/span&gt; मान में&lt;br /&gt;
स्वर - (+3) &lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;स्थितीय&lt;/span&gt; मान में&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;HEA : AHD&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/23/02/F1_SSC_Mrunal_20.02.2023_D25.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 115px; height: 137px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;TER : MHK&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/23/02/F1_SSC_Mrunal_20.02.2023_D26.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 117px; height: 136px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;अतः, सही उत्तर &amp;quot;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;उपर्युक्त में से कोई नहीं&amp;quot;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;है।&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ng-binding&quot; ng-bind-html=&quot;getSol(questionsExtraInfoDetails.q, &#039;en&#039;)&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.testbook.com/images/production/quesImages/qImage437.png&quot; style=&quot;height: 101px; width: 470px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ng-binding&quot; ng-bind-html=&quot;getSol(questionsExtraInfoDetails.q, &#039;en&#039;)&quot;&gt;The logic follows&amp;nbsp;here is:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;COMPUTER is written as RFUVQNPC&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/24/02/F1_teaching_Arbaz_5-2-24_D6.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 467px; height: 257px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;​&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;​similarly,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;MEDICINE be written&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;as:&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/24/02/F1_teaching_Arbaz_5-2-24_D7.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 470px; height: 257px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Hence, the correct answer is&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;EOJDJEFM&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ng-binding&quot; ng-bind-html=&quot;getSol(questionsExtraInfoDetails.q, &#039;en&#039;)&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.testbook.com/images/production/quesImages/qImage437.png&quot; style=&quot;height: 101px; width: 470px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;यहाँ तर्क इस प्रकार है:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;COMPUTER&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;को RFUVQNPC लिखा जाता है&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/24/02/F1_teaching_Arbaz_5-2-24_D6.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 467px; height: 257px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;​&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;​इसी तरह,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;MEDICINE&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;को इस प्रकार लिखा जाए:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/24/02/F1_teaching_Arbaz_5-2-24_D7.png&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-weight: 700; width: 470px; height: 257px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;अतः सही उत्तर &lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;EOJDJEFM&amp;quot;&lt;/strong&gt; है।&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Family Chart:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/images/production/quesImages/qImage13914.png&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Given:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;T is the mother of S&amp;#39;s father.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;U is the wife of S.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;V is the only son of W who is married to T.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;X is the daughter of U.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Y is the brother of X and married to Z.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/24/01/F2_SSC_Savita_23-01-24_D5.png&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41); width: 311px; height: 270px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;So, S&amp;nbsp;is &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Husband&amp;#39;s father&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;of Z.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Hence, the correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;Option 2&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;वंश आरेख:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/images/production/quesImages/qImage13914.png&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;दिया गया है:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;T, S के पिता की माता&amp;nbsp;है।&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;U, S की पत्नी है.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;V, W का इकलौता पुत्र है जिसका विवाह T से हुआ है।&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;X, U की पुत्री&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;है।&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Y, X का भाई है और उसका विवाह Z से हुआ है।&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/24/01/F2_SSC_Savita_23-01-24_D5.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 311px; height: 270px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;इसलिए, S, Z के &amp;#39;पति का पिता&amp;#39; है।&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;अतः, सही उत्तर &lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;विकल्प 2&amp;quot;&lt;/strong&gt; है.&lt;/p&gt;

