questions.statement:
&lt;p&gt;Which two signs should be interchanged to make the given equation correct?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;167 + 85 &amp;ndash; 5 &amp;times; 4 &amp;divide; 36 = 199&lt;/p&gt;<br>&lt;p&gt;दिए गए समीकरण को सही बनाने के लिए किन दो चिह्नों&amp;nbsp;को आपस में बदला जाना चाहिए?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;167 + 85 &amp;ndash; 5 &amp;times; 4 &amp;divide; 36 = 199&lt;/p&gt;

questions.explanation:
&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/23/08/6203fea433474e3b330f0951_22-7-22_Shashi%20Savita_D1.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 368px; height: 193px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Let&amp;#39;s check each option,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;Given Equation:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&amp;nbsp;167 + 85 &amp;ndash; 5 &amp;times; 4 &amp;divide; 36 = 199&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;1) &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;divide; and &amp;times;&amp;nbsp;&amp;rarr;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;rarr;&amp;nbsp;167 + 85 &amp;ndash; 5 &amp;divide; 4 &amp;times;&amp;nbsp;36 = 199&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;rarr;&amp;nbsp;167 + 85 &amp;ndash; 45&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;= 199&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;rarr; 252 &amp;ndash; 45&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;= 199&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

